113
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,600
By the way, Mai Xiang.

114
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,360
Yes?

115
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,920
Do you remember what medicine

116
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,400
Mrs. Tang needs?

117
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:47,160
Do you want to deliver medicine to her?

118
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:47,680
Yes.

119
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,760
The mountain path there
is very difficult to walk.

120
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,960
It's in the deep mountains.

121
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:54,040
Mrs. Tang's son

122
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:56,640
offered one tael for a bowl
of decoction delivered.

123
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,280
Yes.

124
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,680
The more

125
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:00,200
