130
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:09,640
Alright.

131
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,880
I'll go get the prescription.

132
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:11,360
Okay.

133
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,480
He's still copying books?

134
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,400
Poor brother-in-law.

135
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:20,280
Brother-in-law?

136
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,000
Nonsense.

137
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,280
Mai Tian.

138
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:52,320
Why are you here?

139
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,000
What's wrong?

140
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,400
Twisted your ankle?

141
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,480
Let me check. Come on.

142
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,520
Why are you here?

143
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:04,960
I...

144
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,240
I was passing by.

145
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,280
What are you doing here?

146
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:13,920
I am here to earn more money.

147
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,280
Well,

148
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,440
