177
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:03,880
Sell these instead.

178
00:10:04,600 --> 00:10:05,320
Before,

179
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:08,520
I was afraid Ye Wuming would find out
his identity, so I buried them all.

180
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:11,080
Now we need money,

181
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,760
