182
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,360
That's my girl,

183
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,480
so clever

184
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,240
and capable.

185
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,200
Right.

186
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,080
