236
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:30,680
What's wrong?

237
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:36,920
Ye Wuming.

238
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,560
Calm down.

239
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,800
Calm down.

240
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,600
