241
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,680
so you would be fine, right?

242
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,280
Ye Wuming.

243
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:05,680
I'm sorry.

244
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:08,000
I didn't mean to.

245
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,600
I can't control myself.

246
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,480
I'm feeling so hot.

247
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:13,280
Ye Wuming.

248
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,360
Where are you going?

249
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:16,480
Don't stop me.

250
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:18,080
I'm afraid I can't control myself.

251
00:13:52,928 --> 00:13:55,250
♪The wind drifts alone and free♪

252
00:13:56,856 --> 00:13:59,904
♪Through seasons, none asks of me♪

253
00:14:01,952 --> 00:14:04,775
