254
00:14:06,016 --> 00:14:09,523
♪Only the waning moon
lights my solitude♪

255
00:14:11,296 --> 00:14:13,950
♪Love arose with the wind's sigh♪

256
00:14:15,365 --> 00:14:19,017
♪On a cold night,
a swan's shadow flashes by♪

257
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,208
