264
00:14:43,083 --> 00:14:46,944
♪Seeking spring's song
and night whispers♪

265
00:14:46,944 --> 00:14:49,984
♪Long autumn comes,
and wild geese southward fly♪

266
00:14:49,984 --> 00:14:52,866
♪The azure clouds know my name♪

267
00:14:52,866 --> 00:14:56,288
♪I remember you, and you understand me♪

268
00:14:56,288 --> 00:14:59,136
♪Watching the sun set♪

269
00:14:59,248 --> 00:15:02,112
♪Autumn departs, and beauty fades away♪

270
